---
const { title } = Astro.props
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24">

  <!-- Background accent -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
    <img src="/wallpapers/blackspike-wallpaper-03.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-10" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-bs-surface-1 via-bs-surface-1/95 to-bs-surface-0"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="bs-container relative grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.9fr)_minmax(0,1.1fr)] items-center">

    <!-- Portrait -->
    <figure class="relative order-last lg:order-first">
      <div class="absolute -inset-6 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-bs-primary/20 via-transparent to-bs-secondary/15 blur-3xl" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-bs-surface-3/70 bg-bs-surface-2/50 backdrop-blur">
        <img src="/content-images/quote-man.avif" alt="BastCo founder speaking at a cybersecurity conference" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-bs-surface-1 via-transparent"></div>
      </div>
    </figure>

    <!-- Copy -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-bs-secondary">
          Our Story
        </span>
        <h2 class="bs-h2">{ title }</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-bs-surface-2/70 border border-bs-surface-3/60 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-lg shadow-black/20 space-y-4">
        <p class="bs-body-text text-lg text-bs-foreground-dark leading-relaxed">
          Founded by leading experts in Cybersecurity & software engineering, We are dedicated to providing innovative solutions. We believe in building strong relationships with our clients, founded on trust and a deep understanding of their challenges. Our mission is to empower businesses to thrive securely in a digital-first world.
        </p>
        <p class="bs-body-text text-bs-foreground-dark/90 leading-relaxed">
          From red-team simulations to enterprise DevSecOps rollouts, our specialists operate as an embedded extension of your organizationâ€”ensuring security is an enabler, not a bottleneck.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-bs-foreground-dark">
        <img src="/content-images/logo-06.svg" alt="BastCo badge" class="h-10 w-auto" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-bs-foreground-light">Headquartered in Texas & Nairobi, working globally</p>
          <p>Trusted partners for finance, healthcare, and public sector teams.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>
